TimestampedBoolean
==================

Use timestamps for boolean columns.


Example
=======

class User < ActiveRecord::Base
  include TimestampedBoolean

  timestamped_boolean :active
end

u = User.new
u.active = true
u.active_changed_at #=> Tue May 19 15:53:29 -0400 2009


